*Korak* po korak, on je napredovao. (He advanced step by step.)

On je učinio veliki *korak* ka uspehu. (He made a big step towards success.)

Ona je išla *koraka* neznanja. (She was going the step of ignorance.)

On je polako ali sigurno pravio *korake* ka napretku. (He was slowly but surely making steps towards progress.)

Ona je stala na *korak* pred cilj. (She stood one step away from the goal.)